{
  "text": "We show the smoothing performance with different orders and different \u03b1 parameters in Fig. 2 . We use Canny detector to obtain the initial edges (Fig. 2b) and then modify them to meet the \"n active\" criterion to get our edge weights. We use the spatially varying smoothness weights in [CITATION_1] (Fig. 2c) :",
  "citation_candidates": [
